data.description: *** One level living with all the conveniences sums up this 2017 three Bedroom, two full Bath, Singleton design by E.G. Stoltzfus. Kitchen comes complete with an eat-in area, a gas range, double sink, and built-in dishwasher. The primary suite is located on the opposite side of home from the other two bedrooms. It includes a walk-in closet and private full bathroom. A first  floor laundry, oversized two car garage, covered front porch, plus a fully fenced back yard are just some of the many wonderful features. You have to see this fenced, level, corner lot in Ashley Farms community! Low yearly HOA fee with minimal restrictions. Restaurants, entertainment, and just about anything you could ever need is just a short drive away. This one won't last long so schedule your showing today***Open House has been canceled due to being under contract.
